OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will
OL,6,Fremain cloudy through the evening and
OL,7,Fovernight with some showery outbreaks
OL,8,Fof rain, some of these will be heavy
OL,9,Fat first, gradually easing overnight.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSunday:FDull and cloudy through the
OL,12,Fmorning with a few light showers.
OL,13,FBrighter spells developing later in
OL,14,Fthe day.
OL,15,
OL,16,COutlook for Monday to Wednesday:FRain
OL,17,Ffor a time on Monday then bright
OL,18,Fspells and showers continuing through
OL,19,FTuesday and Wednesday. Remaining
OL,20,Fcooler with some overnight frost.
